{"title":"枫树","authors":["徐振武"],"dates":[{"year":1994,"month":6,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"枫树"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"徐振武"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在淅沥沥的秋雨中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欣然开启三月里封存的记忆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"点燃绿色的爱恋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾用稚嫩的语言，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"编织过春的童话——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"根，游入深深的泥土；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叶，飞向蔚蓝的天空，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被阳光扶直的脊梁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无私地擎起一团清凉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光很灿烂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夏季热烈而蓬勃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树前一弯小溪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流出遍地翠韵……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"郁郁葱葱的回忆里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也有风雨留下的伤瘢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今那些磨砺那些曲折，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已被茂密的枝叶覆盖；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成熟为红色的思绪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一种风霜涂抹不掉的温馨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越来越强烈……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}